"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-09-beyblade-returns-spinning-tops-become-olympic-sport-21193469\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Competitive spinning tops may sound absurd but it's one of the most popular toy brands in the world and it's about to make a big comeback.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 138, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Competitive spinning tops\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 25}, {\"ngram\": \"the most popular toy brands\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 86}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 90, \"to\": 99}, {\"ngram\": \"a big comeback\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From Rubik's Cube to Tamagotchi, history is not short of peculiartoysthat you would have sworn kids would never be interested in\\u2026 until they become a multi-million dollar empire.\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 161, \"end\": 171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamagotchi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tamagotchi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamagotchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tamagotchi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rubik's Cube\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 157}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 180}, {\"ngram\": \"peculiartoysthat\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 213}, {\"ngram\": \"a multi-million dollar empire\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyblade is a line of competitive spinning tops, which sounds like a joke until you learn it's sold more than 160 million toys since 1999.\", \"from\": 319, \"to\": 457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 319, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a line\", \"from\": 331, \"to\": 337}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive spinning tops\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 366}, {\"ngram\": \"a joke\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 392}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 160 million toys\", \"from\": 419, \"to\": 445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like many toy lines, it at first seemed to be a fad.\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many toy lines\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"a fad\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But interest never died off completely, particularly in its homeland ofJapan, and now creators Takara Tomy are preparing a relaunch of the brand worldwide.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 607, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takara Tomy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 524}, {\"ngram\": \"its homeland\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"now creators\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"a relaunch\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"the brand\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 656}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is to be a new anime series and new toy gimmicks but the core appeal remains the same: pitting spinning top against spinning top in a plastic arena, in a test of skill and luck which some fans take very seriously indeed.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a new anime series\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"new toy gimmicks\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 722}, {\"ngram\": \"the core appeal\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 742}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 781}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"a plastic arena\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"a test\", \"from\": 826, \"to\": 832}, {\"ngram\": \"skill\", \"from\": 836, \"to\": 841}, {\"ngram\": \"luck\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"some fans\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 866}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although the core audience is still children, those that were playing in the early 2000s now have kids of their own, as well as an urge to keep playing themselves.\", \"from\": 896, \"to\": 1059, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the core audience\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 922}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"the early 2000s\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 998}, {\"ngram\": \"an urge\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1031}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nostalgia is key to the appeal of many toy brands nowadays and as it celebrates its 25th anniversary, Beyblade is poised to take full advantage of its legacy.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1162, \"end\": 1170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nostalgia\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"the appeal\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"many toy brands\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1109}, {\"ngram\": \"its 25th anniversary\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1160}, {\"ngram\": \"full advantage\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"its legacy\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In the beginning it was solely geared towards children and for them to have fun as a toy,' designer Kenji Horikoshi told Metro, during a visit to Japanese toy company Takara Tomy.\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenji_Yoshida\", \"score\": 0.9993924082621978, \"rank\": 0.000607920109123528, \"text\": \"Kenji\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenji_Yoshida\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenji_Yoshida\"}, {\"begin\": 1367, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"score\": 0.9999839483085905, \"rank\": 1.2986196964224032e-05, \"text\": \"Japanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japanese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takara Tomy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1237}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1275}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1300}, {\"ngram\": \"a toy\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"Metro\", \"from\": 1342, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"a visit\", \"from\": 1356, \"to\": 1363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But as time went on more adults were able to find joy in playing Beyblade as well.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1467, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"more adults\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1455}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so that became more of a competitive feel.'\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a competitive feel\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before they merged with Tomy (who have their 100th anniversary this year), Takara were the original creators of The Transformers (which in turn is currently celebrating its 40th anniversary).\", \"from\": 1534, \"to\": 1725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1609, \"end\": 1615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"score\": 0.9998997482449732, \"rank\": 0.00010026180602905717, \"text\": \"Takara\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tomy\", \"from\": 1558, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"their 100th anniversary\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"the original creators\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"The Transformers\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"its 40th anniversary\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For both toy lines they partner with American company Hasbro, who adapts them for the West and add their own designs and marketing twists.\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1763, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_American_Company\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"American company\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_American_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_American_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 1780, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hasbro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both toy lines\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"the West\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"their own designs\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1842}, {\"ngram\": \"marketing twists\", \"from\": 1847, \"to\": 1863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'As those kids became older, those that grew up with Beyblade are now adults and there is this whole cycle of kids that are now interacting with Beyblade for the first time but alongside adults that also still play with Beyblade, which has led to it becoming naturally more competitive,' explains Horikoshi.\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1919, \"end\": 1927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 2011, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 2086, \"end\": 2094, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"those kids\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"this whole cycle\", \"from\": 1956, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1980}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 2024, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2059}, {\"ngram\": \"Horikoshi\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In order to play Beyblade, all you need is a spinning top and launcher, and ideally a plastic *Beystadium* to drop them into - which has groves on the edges to encourage the tops to move around in a circle, as well as traps for the tops to fall into and put them out of play.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2192, \"end\": 2200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2178, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"a spinning top\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"ideally a plastic\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2268}, {\"ngram\": \"Beystadium\", \"from\": 2270, \"to\": 2280}, {\"ngram\": \"groves\", \"from\": 2312, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"the edges\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2331}, {\"ngram\": \"the tops\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"a circle\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2380}, {\"ngram\": \"the tops\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2411}, {\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 2445, \"to\": 2449}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To start, you simply place the top into the launcher and both players release them at the same time, at which point you just watch and see what happens.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"the launcher\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"both players\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2520}, {\"ngram\": \"the same time\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2550}, {\"ngram\": \"which point\", \"from\": 2555, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It sounds as if there is nothing to it, but that's clearly not the case, given how good some players have got at it - with national tournaments organised across the global and international championship planned for later this year.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2836, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2637}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"some players\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2705}, {\"ngram\": \"national tournaments\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"the global and international championship\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"later this year\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What exactly these elite players are doing to perform so consistently I am not sure, but no doubt it's all in the wrist.\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2957, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these elite players\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrist\", \"from\": 2947, \"to\": 2956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It brings to mind the famous British court case, in 1908, where it was proven that darts was not a game of chance and required skill to do well at, with an expert player of the day being asked to throw three 20s in a row in the courtroom.\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 3197, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2988, \"end\": 2995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 3.242921160573937e-12, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"darts\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3047}, {\"ngram\": \"a game\", \"from\": 3056, \"to\": 3062}, {\"ngram\": \"chance\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"skill\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"an expert player\", \"from\": 3112, \"to\": 3128}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"three 20s\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3170}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"the courtroom\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Beyblade equivalent of this test is to play anyone that knows what they are doing.\", \"from\": 3198, \"to\": 3284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3202, \"end\": 3210, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this test\", \"from\": 3225, \"to\": 3234}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which is another way of saying I lost every battle I competed in.\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3350, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another way\", \"from\": 3294, \"to\": 3305}, {\"ngram\": \"every battle\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You soon learn that preparation is key, with each top being composed of three separate components that are colour-coded for attack, defence, stamina, and balance.\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3514, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that preparation\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3383}, {\"ngram\": \"each top\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"three separate components\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3449}, {\"ngram\": \"attack\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3482}, {\"ngram\": \"defence\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3491}, {\"ngram\": \"stamina\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3500}, {\"ngram\": \"balance\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3513}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These can be mixed and matched however you want, to create a hybrid spinning top, although there is some complication when it comes to different generations of Beyblade, some of which have overpowered parts.\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3722, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3675, \"end\": 3683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hybrid spinning top\", \"from\": 3574, \"to\": 3595}, {\"ngram\": \"some complication\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3632}, {\"ngram\": \"different generations\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3671}, {\"ngram\": \"overpowered parts\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In tournament battles this means the adjudicators have to carefully examine each top before it's allowed to compete, as they adjust the scoring system so that one built with overpowered parts has a points handicap.\", \"from\": 3724, \"to\": 3938, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tournament battles\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3745}, {\"ngram\": \"the adjudicators\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3773}, {\"ngram\": \"each top\", \"from\": 3800, \"to\": 3808}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoring system\", \"from\": 3856, \"to\": 3874}, {\"ngram\": \"overpowered parts\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3915}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the competitors we watched risked instant failure, by using a very overpowered top, so that if he lost even one round he was out, but few were that brave.\", \"from\": 3939, \"to\": 4100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the competitors\", \"from\": 3946, \"to\": 3961}, {\"ngram\": \"instant failure\", \"from\": 3980, \"to\": 3995}, {\"ngram\": \"a very overpowered top\", \"from\": 4006, \"to\": 4028}, {\"ngram\": \"even one round\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was invited to watch a local tournament and it was fascinating to see the split between younger and older players, all competing together in apparent harmony.\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a local tournament\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4143}, {\"ngram\": \"the split\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4183}, {\"ngram\": \"younger and older players\", \"from\": 4192, \"to\": 4217}, {\"ngram\": \"apparent harmony\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although it was the kids that were showing the most obvious signs of excitement.\", \"from\": 4263, \"to\": 4343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 4279, \"to\": 4287}, {\"ngram\": \"the most obvious signs\", \"from\": 4306, \"to\": 4328}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One girl, who could not have been more than six years old, joined other younger elements of the crowd in screaming the phrase '3, 2, 1, Go Shoot!'\", \"from\": 4344, \"to\": 4490, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One girl\", \"from\": 4344, \"to\": 4352}, {\"ngram\": \"other younger elements\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4432}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4445}, {\"ngram\": \"the phrase\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"that proceeds each battle.\", \"from\": 4491, \"to\": 4517, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each battle\", \"from\": 4505, \"to\": 4516}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All the kids were cheering on the players as if watching their favourite sports team, which is exactly the sort of attitude Takara Tomy want to encourage.\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4643, \"end\": 4654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takara Tomy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the kids\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4531}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4560}, {\"ngram\": \"their favourite sports team\", \"from\": 4576, \"to\": 4603}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly the sort\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4630}, {\"ngram\": \"attitude\", \"from\": 4634, \"to\": 4642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a long while though, there has not been any physical tournaments, thanks to Covid, which created a major problem for Beyblade, since it's very much an in-person social experience.\", \"from\": 4675, \"to\": 4858, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4796, \"end\": 4804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long while\", \"from\": 4679, \"to\": 4691}, {\"ngram\": \"any physical tournaments\", \"from\": 4719, \"to\": 4743}, {\"ngram\": \"thanks\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4751}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4760}, {\"ngram\": \"a major problem\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4791}, {\"ngram\": \"an in-person social experience\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Horikoshi explains that Takara Tomy were forced to experiment with online tournaments and that, surprisingly, it proved very popular.\", \"from\": 4859, \"to\": 4992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4883, \"end\": 4894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takara Tomy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Horikoshi\", \"from\": 4859, \"to\": 4868}, {\"ngram\": \"online tournaments\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Teaming up with YouTubers specialising in Beyblade they have also expanded to other online arenas, with the official Beyblade section of Roblox seeing 4.5 million visitors during lockdown.\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5182, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5010, \"end\": 5019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.017870971214453e-15, \"text\": \"YouTubers\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/YouTube\"}, {\"begin\": 5036, \"end\": 5044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 5111, \"end\": 5119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 5131, \"end\": 5137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roblox\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roblox\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other online arenas\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5091}, {\"ngram\": \"4.5 million visitors\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5165}, {\"ngram\": \"lockdown\", \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5181}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Japan there is even been cross-promotion with one of Tokyo's biggest baseball teams.\", \"from\": 5183, \"to\": 5270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5186, \"end\": 5191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999997740369764, \"rank\": 1.4509426447064745e-07, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 5239, \"end\": 5244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.999999985087925, \"rank\": 8.098809003302513e-09, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"promotion\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5226}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The pandemic was really rough for everyone, but fans were able to really understand and appreciate the Beyblade community and with tournaments making a comeback a lot more fans are becoming a lot more engaged and coming to these areas where they can interact with each other,' says Horikoshi.\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5376, \"end\": 5384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pandemic\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5285}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5307, \"to\": 5315}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5325}, {\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 5404, \"to\": 5415}, {\"ngram\": \"a comeback\", \"from\": 5423, \"to\": 5433}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot more fans\", \"from\": 5434, \"to\": 5449}, {\"ngram\": \"these areas\", \"from\": 5496, \"to\": 5507}, {\"ngram\": \"Horikoshi\", \"from\": 5555, \"to\": 5564}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That forced push into embracing online has worked out for the best, with the tactile pleasures of the game now augmented by an app that has been downloaded 50 million times in Japan.\", \"from\": 5567, \"to\": 5749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5743, \"end\": 5748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999997740369764, \"rank\": 1.4509426447064745e-07, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"push\", \"from\": 5579, \"to\": 5583}, {\"ngram\": \"the tactile pleasures\", \"from\": 5640, \"to\": 5661}, {\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 5665, \"to\": 5673}, {\"ngram\": \"an app\", \"from\": 5691, \"to\": 5697}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed, you could see many of the players at the tournament with a strange device on their launcher that I initially took to be some sort of motorised ripcord but was in fact a stat tracker to connect to the app, to study details like the exact speed and duration of a spin.\", \"from\": 5750, \"to\": 6024, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 5780, \"to\": 5791}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 5795, \"to\": 5809}, {\"ngram\": \"a strange device\", \"from\": 5815, \"to\": 5831}, {\"ngram\": \"their launcher\", \"from\": 5835, \"to\": 5849}, {\"ngram\": \"some sort\", \"from\": 5878, \"to\": 5887}, {\"ngram\": \"motorised ripcord\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5908}, {\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 5920, \"to\": 5924}, {\"ngram\": \"a stat tracker\", \"from\": 5925, \"to\": 5939}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 5954, \"to\": 5961}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 5972, \"to\": 5979}, {\"ngram\": \"the exact speed\", \"from\": 5985, \"to\": 6000}, {\"ngram\": \"duration\", \"from\": 6005, \"to\": 6013}, {\"ngram\": \"a spin\", \"from\": 6017, \"to\": 6023}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyblade is serious business for some people, but the fandom extends beyond just the toys, to highly successful manga and anime series as well.\", \"from\": 6026, \"to\": 6169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6026, \"end\": 6034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"serious business\", \"from\": 6038, \"to\": 6054}, {\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 6059, \"to\": 6070}, {\"ngram\": \"the fandom\", \"from\": 6076, \"to\": 6086}, {\"ngram\": \"just the toys\", \"from\": 6102, \"to\": 6115}, {\"ngram\": \"highly successful manga and anime series\", \"from\": 6120, \"to\": 6160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These parallel the changes in the toy line, with Takara Tomy already having launched the fourth generation in Japan and Hasbro recently following suit in the West.\", \"from\": 6170, \"to\": 6333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6219, \"end\": 6230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takara Tomy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\"}, {\"begin\": 6280, \"end\": 6285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9999997740369764, \"rank\": 1.4509426447064745e-07, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 6290, \"end\": 6296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hasbro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 6185, \"to\": 6196}, {\"ngram\": \"the toy line\", \"from\": 6200, \"to\": 6212}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth generation\", \"from\": 6255, \"to\": 6276}, {\"ngram\": \"suit\", \"from\": 6316, \"to\": 6320}, {\"ngram\": \"the West\", \"from\": 6324, \"to\": 6332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Perhaps the most surprising thing about Beyblade is that it's not actually that expensive.\", \"from\": 6335, \"to\": 6425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6375, \"end\": 6383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most surprising thing\", \"from\": 6343, \"to\": 6368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can get everything you need for a battle for less than \\u00a350, although of course the more you get into it the more you are likely to spend on additional spinning tops, to mix and match their parts.\", \"from\": 6426, \"to\": 6625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 6438, \"to\": 6448}, {\"ngram\": \"a battle\", \"from\": 6462, \"to\": 6470}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 6502, \"to\": 6508}, {\"ngram\": \"additional spinning tops\", \"from\": 6570, \"to\": 6594}, {\"ngram\": \"their parts\", \"from\": 6613, \"to\": 6624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That green stripe is the X-Celerator Rail (Hasbro) Beyblade X Xtreme Battle Set- \\u00a344.99This is the obvious place to start as it includes two fourth generation Beyblade X tops, a Beystadium with the X-Celerator rail, and two launchers with ripcords.\", \"from\": 6627, \"to\": 6876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6670, \"end\": 6676, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hasbro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\"}, {\"begin\": 6679, \"end\": 6687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 6787, \"end\": 6795, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"That green stripe\", \"from\": 6627, \"to\": 6644}, {\"ngram\": \"the obvious place\", \"from\": 6722, \"to\": 6739}, {\"ngram\": \"a Beystadium\", \"from\": 6803, \"to\": 6815}, {\"ngram\": \"the X-Celerator rail\", \"from\": 6821, \"to\": 6841}, {\"ngram\": \"two launchers\", \"from\": 6847, \"to\": 6860}, {\"ngram\": \"ripcords\", \"from\": 6866, \"to\": 6874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's all you need to play and while only having a single top each means you will be short on pre-match strategy options this is a cheap way to see whether you and your kids enjoy the concept.\", \"from\": 6877, \"to\": 7070, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a single top\", \"from\": 6927, \"to\": 6939}, {\"ngram\": \"pre-match strategy options\", \"from\": 6972, \"to\": 6998}, {\"ngram\": \"a cheap way\", \"from\": 7007, \"to\": 7018}, {\"ngram\": \"your kids\", \"from\": 7042, \"to\": 7051}, {\"ngram\": \"the concept\", \"from\": 7058, \"to\": 7069}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ripcord or string are the two big launcher choices (Hasbro) Beyblade X Soar Phoenix Deluxe String Launcher Set- \\u00a319.99If you start getting into Beyblade then this is the next obvious step, as it includes a new top and an alternative string launcher.\", \"from\": 7072, \"to\": 7322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7072, \"end\": 7079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacy_X\", \"score\": 0.9999999831734386, \"rank\": 8.15232282755793e-09, \"text\": \"Ripcord\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacy_X\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stacy_X\"}, {\"begin\": 7124, \"end\": 7130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hasbro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\"}, {\"begin\": 7133, \"end\": 7141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 7217, \"end\": 7225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"string\", \"from\": 7083, \"to\": 7089}, {\"ngram\": \"the two big launcher choices\", \"from\": 7094, \"to\": 7122}, {\"ngram\": \"the next obvious step\", \"from\": 7238, \"to\": 7259}, {\"ngram\": \"a new top\", \"from\": 7276, \"to\": 7285}, {\"ngram\": \"an alternative string launcher\", \"from\": 7290, \"to\": 7320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which launcher you use seems to be a matter of preference but neither option gives an unfair advantage.\", \"from\": 7323, \"to\": 7426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Which launcher\", \"from\": 7323, \"to\": 7337}, {\"ngram\": \"a matter\", \"from\": 7358, \"to\": 7366}, {\"ngram\": \"preference\", \"from\": 7370, \"to\": 7380}, {\"ngram\": \"neither option\", \"from\": 7385, \"to\": 7399}, {\"ngram\": \"an unfair advantage\", \"from\": 7406, \"to\": 7425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The colours are very important (Hasbro) Starter Pack Sets- \\u00a39.99 eachExtra spinning tops are sold separately and have names like Arrow Wizard 4-80B and Scythe Incendio 4-60T.\", \"from\": 7428, \"to\": 7603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The colours\", \"from\": 7428, \"to\": 7439}, {\"ngram\": \"very important (Hasbro) Starter Pack Sets-\", \"from\": 7444, \"to\": 7486}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00a39.99 eachExtra spinning tops\", \"from\": 7487, \"to\": 7516}, {\"ngram\": \"names\", \"from\": 7546, \"to\": 7551}, {\"ngram\": \"Arrow Wizard\", \"from\": 7557, \"to\": 7569}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No matter the generation they can all be taken apart and put together again in any combination, with the three separate parts each being colour-coded according to whether they are designed for attack, defence, stamina, and balance.\", \"from\": 7604, \"to\": 7835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the generation\", \"from\": 7614, \"to\": 7628}, {\"ngram\": \"any combination\", \"from\": 7683, \"to\": 7698}, {\"ngram\": \"the three separate parts\", \"from\": 7705, \"to\": 7729}, {\"ngram\": \"attack\", \"from\": 7797, \"to\": 7803}, {\"ngram\": \"defence\", \"from\": 7805, \"to\": 7812}, {\"ngram\": \"stamina\", \"from\": 7814, \"to\": 7821}, {\"ngram\": \"balance\", \"from\": 7827, \"to\": 7834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The new gimmick for the fourth generation is 'super acceleration' on all the new spinning tops, which is enabled by the new X-Celerator rail on the Beystadium - a toothed railing along the perimeter of the arena that can speed up tops even faster.\", \"from\": 7837, \"to\": 8084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The new gimmick\", \"from\": 7837, \"to\": 7852}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth generation\", \"from\": 7857, \"to\": 7878}, {\"ngram\": \"super acceleration\", \"from\": 7883, \"to\": 7901}, {\"ngram\": \"all the new spinning tops\", \"from\": 7906, \"to\": 7931}, {\"ngram\": \"the new X-Celerator rail\", \"from\": 7953, \"to\": 7977}, {\"ngram\": \"the Beystadium\", \"from\": 7981, \"to\": 7995}, {\"ngram\": \"a toothed railing\", \"from\": 7998, \"to\": 8015}, {\"ngram\": \"the perimeter\", \"from\": 8022, \"to\": 8035}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 8039, \"to\": 8048}, {\"ngram\": \"tops\", \"from\": 8067, \"to\": 8071}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the same though, there is an attempt to feed into the nostalgia of the 25th anniversary, with many of the older sets and gimmicks also being brought back.\", \"from\": 8086, \"to\": 8243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 8115, \"to\": 8125}, {\"ngram\": \"the nostalgia\", \"from\": 8139, \"to\": 8152}, {\"ngram\": \"the 25th anniversary\", \"from\": 8156, \"to\": 8176}, {\"ngram\": \"the older sets\", \"from\": 8191, \"to\": 8205}, {\"ngram\": \"gimmicks\", \"from\": 8210, \"to\": 8218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A new generation also means a new anime series, called Beyblade X, which will come to UK screens later this year.\", \"from\": 8244, \"to\": 8357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8299, \"end\": 8307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 8330, \"end\": 8332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999972221923982, \"rank\": 2.7778099384205215e-06, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A new generation\", \"from\": 8244, \"to\": 8260}, {\"ngram\": \"a new anime series\", \"from\": 8272, \"to\": 8290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'We were very confident with our toys and having that face-to-face interaction.\", \"from\": 8359, \"to\": 8438, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our toys\", \"from\": 8388, \"to\": 8396}, {\"ngram\": \"face\", \"from\": 8421, \"to\": 8425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although there is this metaverse digital element, that is present in the modern day, we are confident that we will continue to innovate them both.\", \"from\": 8439, \"to\": 8585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this metaverse digital element\", \"from\": 8457, \"to\": 8487}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern day\", \"from\": 8508, \"to\": 8522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, we will have the digital element and also the physical element, and that is going to be the new formula as we continue to grow.'\", \"from\": 8586, \"to\": 8718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the digital element\", \"from\": 8603, \"to\": 8622}, {\"ngram\": \"also the physical element\", \"from\": 8627, \"to\": 8652}, {\"ngram\": \"the new formula\", \"from\": 8678, \"to\": 8693}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than once, we hear Takara Tomy and Hasbro staff joke about making Beyblade an Olympic sport, but it's clear that there is at least a kernel of honest hope that it could one day happen\\u2026 perhaps for the 50th anniversary.\", \"from\": 8720, \"to\": 8943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8744, \"end\": 8755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Takara Tomy\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tomy\"}, {\"begin\": 8760, \"end\": 8766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hasbro\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasbro\"}, {\"begin\": 8791, \"end\": 8799, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"at least a kernel\", \"from\": 8847, \"to\": 8864}, {\"ngram\": \"honest hope\", \"from\": 8868, \"to\": 8879}, {\"ngram\": \"one day\", \"from\": 8894, \"to\": 8901}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50th anniversary\", \"from\": 8922, \"to\": 8942}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the very least, they are open about their ambitions for Beyblade to be accepted alongside other 'gear-assisted' sports like golf and skateboarding.\", \"from\": 8944, \"to\": 9094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9003, \"end\": 9011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their ambitions\", \"from\": 8983, \"to\": 8998}, {\"ngram\": \"other 'gear-assisted' sports\", \"from\": 9037, \"to\": 9065}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 9071, \"to\": 9075}, {\"ngram\": \"skateboarding\", \"from\": 9080, \"to\": 9093}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Our mission here is to make sure we continue innovating and as the years progress, even without it being an Olympic sport, we just want to make sure people globally can have a chance to really appreciate and play with each other and have that competitive feel.'\", \"from\": 9096, \"to\": 9358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our mission\", \"from\": 9097, \"to\": 9108}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 9160, \"to\": 9169}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic sport\", \"from\": 9202, \"to\": 9218}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 9246, \"to\": 9252}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 9271, \"to\": 9279}, {\"ngram\": \"that competitive feel\", \"from\": 9335, \"to\": 9356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Spinning tops as a serious sport may seem absurd but to a child it's conceptually no different to darts or golf.\", \"from\": 9360, \"to\": 9472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Spinning tops\", \"from\": 9360, \"to\": 9373}, {\"ngram\": \"a serious sport\", \"from\": 9377, \"to\": 9392}, {\"ngram\": \"a child\", \"from\": 9416, \"to\": 9423}, {\"ngram\": \"darts\", \"from\": 9458, \"to\": 9463}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 9467, \"to\": 9471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But whether it gets mainstream recognition or not it does not really matter, as Beyblade's success has been evident for decades now and as Beyblade X puts a new spin on things, it's attempting to attract a bigger audience than ever.\", \"from\": 9473, \"to\": 9705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 9553, \"end\": 9561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}, {\"begin\": 9612, \"end\": 9620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.861770989473264e-55, \"text\": \"Beyblade\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beyblade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mainstream recognition\", \"from\": 9493, \"to\": 9515}, {\"ngram\": \"decades\", \"from\": 9593, \"to\": 9600}, {\"ngram\": \"a new spin\", \"from\": 9628, \"to\": 9638}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 9642, \"to\": 9648}, {\"ngram\": \"a bigger audience\", \"from\": 9677, \"to\": 9694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Got a story?\", \"from\": 9707, \"to\": 9719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a story\", \"from\": 9711, \"to\": 9718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you have got a celebrity story, video or pictures get in touch with theMetro.co.ukentertainment team by emailing us celebtips@metro.co.uk, calling 020 3615 2145 or by visiting ourSubmit Stuffpage - we'd love to hear from you.\", \"from\": 9721, \"to\": 9949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a celebrity story\", \"from\": 9737, \"to\": 9754}, {\"ngram\": \"video\", \"from\": 9756, \"to\": 9761}, {\"ngram\": \"pictures\", \"from\": 9765, \"to\": 9773}, {\"ngram\": \"touch\", \"from\": 9781, \"to\": 9786}, {\"ngram\": \"theMetro.co.ukentertainment team\", \"from\": 9792, \"to\": 9824}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 9837, \"to\": 9839}, {\"ngram\": \"ourSubmit Stuffpage\", \"from\": 9900, \"to\": 9919}]}]}"